        public ReplicationPeerConfigBuilder setTableCFsMap(Map<TableName,List<String>> tableCFsMap)
        从接口复制的说明: ReplicationPeerConfigBuilder
        Sets an explicit map of tables and column families in those tables that should be replicated to the given peer. Use ReplicationPeerConfigBuilder.setReplicateAllUserTables(boolean) to replicate all tables to a peer.
        指定者:
        setTableCFsMap 在接口中 ReplicationPeerConfigBuilder
        参数:

      • setExcludeTableCFsMap

        public ReplicationPeerConfigBuilder setExcludeTableCFsMap(Map<TableName,List<String>> excludeTableCFsMap)
        从接口复制的说明: ReplicationPeerConfigBuilder
        Sets the mapping of table name to column families which should not be replicated. This method sets state which is mutually exclusive to ReplicationPeerConfigBuilder.setTableCFsMap(Map). Invoking this method is only relevant when all user tables are being replicated.
        指定者:
        setExcludeTableCFsMap 在接口中 ReplicationPeerConfigBuilder
        参数:
        excludeTableCFsMap - A mapping of table names to column families which should not be replicated. An empty list of column families implies all families for the table.
        返回:
        this.
